'''瑞波鎮'''（{{lang-my|ရွှေဘိုမြို့နယ်}}，{{lang-en|Shwebo Township}}）為[[緬甸|緬甸]][[實皆省|實皆省]][[瑞波縣|瑞波縣]]的鎮區<ref name="MIMU001">[http://www.burmalibrary.org/docs6/MIMU001_A3_SD%20&%20Township%20Overview.pdf "Myanmar States/Divisions & Townships Overview Map"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.burmalibrary.org/docs6/MIMU001_A3_SD%20%26%20Township%20Overview.pdf |date=20101203160828 }} Myanmar Information Management Unit (MIMU)</ref>。2014年人口266,807人，區域面積1,057.2平方公里<ref name=citypopulation/>。該鎮坐落在[[伊洛瓦底河|伊洛瓦底河]]及{{link-en|穆河|Mu River}}間的平原上，古代王宮[[雍笈牙|雍笈牙王宮]]（King Alaungmintaya）則在該鎮被挖掘出<ref>[http://www.myanmar.gov.mm/ministry/hotel/fact/st_div/sagaing.html "Sagaing Division"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.myanmar.gov.mm/ministry/hotel/fact/st_div/sagaing.html |date=20090814144445 }} Ministry of Hotels & Tourism, Union of Myanmar</ref>。瑞波鎮下分95個村莊。[[瑞波|瑞波]]為瑞波鎮之首府。

==毗鄰==
瑞波鎮位在伊洛瓦底河的西邊，東邊與[[曼德勒省|曼德勒省]][[曼德勒縣|曼德勒縣]][[辛古鎮|辛古鎮]]為界。該鎮北邊接[[欽烏鎮|欽烏鎮]]，南邊接[[韋萊鎮|韋萊鎮]]，西邊接[[迪貝因鎮|迪貝因鎮]]。

==經濟==
最近瑞波鎮因灌溉工程技術，使得該鎮的水稻產量大幅提升，現在一年可種三期稻<ref>[http://gain.fas.usda.gov/Recent%20GAIN%20Publications/Commodity%20Report_GRAIN%20_Rangoon_Burma%20-%20Union%20of_4-29-2009.pdf "Union of Burma - GRAIN Grain and Feed Annual"] {{Wayback|url=http://gain.fas.usda.gov/Recent%20GAIN%20Publications/Commodity%20Report_GRAIN%20_Rangoon_Burma%20-%20Union%20of_4-29-2009.pdf |date=20160303194601 }} p. 3, GAIN Report Number: BM9008, 29 April 2009, Foreign Agricultural Service, United States Department of Agriculture</ref>。

